  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">To study the characteristics of sea stars in a group of tide pools, researchers measured the diameter of the sea stars within the tide pools. The dot plot gives the diameter, to the nearest inch, of each of the sea stars in these tide pools.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><figure class='image'><svg version=\"1.0.0\" width=\"134px\" height=\"149px\" viewBox=\"0 0 134 149\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" aria-label=\"A dot plot. The number line is labeled Diameter (inches). The number line ranges from 16 to 20. Refer to long description.\"><g><g class=\"xtitle-group\" transform=\"translate(67, 129)\"><text class=\"xtitle-group-line-0\" transform=\"translate(0, 0)\" fill=\"currentColor\" style=\"font-family: Noto Serif; font-size: 15px;\" text-anchor=\"middle\" dominant-baseline=\"text-before-edge\">Diameter (inches)</text></g><g class=\"x-axis-group\" fill=\"none\" font-size=\"10\" font-family=\"sans-serif\" text-anchor=\"middle\" transform=\"translate(22.5, 103)\"><g class=\"tick x-tick\" opacity=\"1\" transform=\"translate(0.5,0)\"><line stroke=\"currentColor\" y2=\"6px\" y1=\"-6px\" stroke-width=\"1px\"></line><text fill=\"currentColor\" y=\"9.5\" dy=\"0.71em\" style=\"font-family: Noto Serif; font-size: 15px;\" x=\"0\">16</text></g><g class=\"tick x-tick\" opacity=\"1\" transform=\"translate(22.5,0)\"><line stroke=\"currentColor\" y2=\"6px\" y1=\"-6px\" stroke-width=\"1px\"></line><text fill=\"currentColor\" y=\"9.5\" dy=\"0.71em\" style=\"font-family: Noto Serif; font-size: 15px;\" x=\"0\">17</text></g><g class=\"tick x-tick\" opacity=\"1\" transform=\"translate(44.5,0)\"><line stroke=\"currentColor\" y2=\"6px\" y1=\"-6px\" stroke-width=\"1px\"></line><text fill=\"currentColor\" y=\"9.5\" dy=\"0.71em\" style=\"font-family: Noto Serif; font-size: 15px;\" x=\"0\">18</text></g><g class=\"tick x-tick\" opacity=\"1\" transform=\"translate(66.5,0)\"><line stroke=\"currentColor\" y2=\"6px\" y1=\"-6px\" stroke-width=\"1px\"></line><text fill=\"currentColor\" y=\"9.5\" dy=\"0.71em\" style=\"font-family: Noto Serif; font-size: 15px;\" x=\"0\">19</text></g><g class=\"tick x-tick\" opacity=\"1\" transform=\"translate(88.5,0)\"><line stroke=\"currentColor\" y2=\"6px\" y1=\"-6px\" stroke-width=\"1px\"></line><text fill=\"currentColor\" y=\"9.5\" dy=\"0.71em\" style=\"font-family: Noto Serif; font-size: 15px;\" x=\"0\">20</text></g><line class=\"x-axis-line\" x1=\"-12\" x2=\"100\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1px\"></line><line class=\"x-axis-line\" id=\"x-axis-marker-line\" x1=\"-12\" x2=\"100\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1px\"></line></g><g class=\"dot-group\" transform=\"translate(23,-3)\"><circle cx=\"0\" cy=\"93\" r=\"4px\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle><circle cx=\"0\" cy=\"78\" r=\"4px\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle><circle cx=\"0\" cy=\"63\" r=\"4px\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle><circle cx=\"0\" cy=\"48\" r=\"4px\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle><circle cx=\"0\" cy=\"33\" r=\"4px\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle><circle cx=\"0\" cy=\"18\" r=\"4px\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle><circle cx=\"22\" cy=\"93\" r=\"4px\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle><circle cx=\"22\" cy=\"78\" r=\"4px\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle><circle cx=\"22\" cy=\"63\" r=\"4px\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle><circle cx=\"22\" cy=\"48\" r=\"4px\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle><circle cx=\"44\" cy=\"93\" r=\"4px\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle><circle cx=\"66\" cy=\"93\" r=\"4px\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle><circle cx=\"66\" cy=\"78\" r=\"4px\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle><circle cx=\"88\" cy=\"93\" r=\"4px\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle><circle cx=\"88\" cy=\"78\" r=\"4px\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle><circle cx=\"88\" cy=\"63\" r=\"4px\" fill=\"currentColor\"></circle></g></g></svg><div role=\"region\" aria-label=\"Long description for dot plot\" class=\"sr-only\"><ul>\n<li>The data for the dot plot are as follows:<br/>\n<ul>\n<li>16: 6 dots</li>\n<li>17: 4 dots</li>\n<li>18: 1 dot</li>\n<li>19: 2 dots</li>\n<li>20: 3 dots</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul></div></figure></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Based on the dot plot, how many sea stars had a diameter, to the nearest inch, of <math alttext=\"16\"><mn>16</mn>\n</math> inches?</p>",
